    A7["ZONE_SKIPPED_BACKOFF + infra alert"]
    A8["Загрузка grow_cycle/targets/telemetry/nodes/capabilities/bindings"]
    A9{"DB/API circuit open?"}
    A10["record_zone_error + ZONE_DATA_UNAVAILABLE"]
    A11["restore workflow_phase из zone_events<br/>(если нет в runtime state)"]
    A12{"degraded mode?<br/>(error_streak>=3)"}
    A13["Только health-проверки + degraded signal"]
